{"id":17479439,"date":"2025-07-31T17:47:00","date_gmt":"2025-07-31T12:17:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/?p=17479439"},"modified":"2026-04-06T16:42:34","modified_gmt":"2026-04-06T11:12:34","slug":"online-bcom-professional-acca-accredited","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/online-bcom-professional-acca-accredited","title":{"rendered":"MAHE Online BCom (Professional): Your Fast-Track to ACCA Qualification"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>9 Exemptions. Training for 4 Papers. One Degree That Does It All.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Imagine finishing your BCom degree and walking out the door already exempt from 9 out of 13 ACCA exams \u2013 papers that ordinarily take other candidates one to two additional years to clear. That is exactly what MAHE&#8217;s Online BCom (Professional) program, now ACCA-accredited, makes possible. In a profession where every paper counts, every year saved is a year of earnings gained, and every globally recognised credential opens new doors, this is one of the most strategically designed undergraduate commerce programs available in India today.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_82_2 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/online-bcom-professional-acca-accredited\/#What_Is_ACCA_and_Why_Does_It_Matter\" >What Is ACCA and Why Does It Matter?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/online-bcom-professional-acca-accredited\/#The_ACCA_Qualification_15_Papers_Across_3_Levels\" >The ACCA Qualification: 15 Papers Across 3 Levels<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/online-bcom-professional-acca-accredited\/#How_MAHE_BCom_Professional_Integrates_with_ACCA\" >How MAHE BCom (Professional) Integrates with ACCA<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/online-bcom-professional-acca-accredited\/#Accreditation_Validity_and_What_It_Means_for_You\" >Accreditation Validity and What It Means for You<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/online-bcom-professional-acca-accredited\/#The_Financial_Case_What_MAHE_Saves_You\" >The Financial Case: What MAHE Saves You<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/online-bcom-professional-acca-accredited\/#The_Complete_Pathway_to_Full_ACCA_Membership\" >The Complete Pathway to Full ACCA Membership<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/online-bcom-professional-acca-accredited\/#Career_Opportunities_After_Graduation\" >Career Opportunities After Graduation<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/online-bcom-professional-acca-accredited\/#The_Smartest_Start_to_a_Global_Finance_Career\" >The Smartest Start to a Global Finance Career<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/online-bcom-professional-acca-accredited\/#Frequently_Asked_Questions_FAQs\" >Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_Is_ACCA_and_Why_Does_It_Matter\"><\/span><strong>What Is ACCA and Why Does It Matter?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The Association of Chartered Certified Accountants (ACCA) is the world&#8217;s largest global professional accounting body, headquartered in the UK. With over 247,000 members and 526,000 students across 181 countries, it is the most internationally recognised accounting qualification in the world. ACCA-qualified professionals are in demand not just in the UK and Europe but across major financial hubs including the UAE, Singapore, Canada, Australia, and India&#8217;s Big 4 firms. The qualification covers business strategy, ethics, governance, financial management, audit, and advanced reporting, making its holders genuinely versatile finance professionals.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For commerce students in India, the question has historically been: do I pursue BCom first and then ACCA separately, spending additional years and money? MAHE&#8217;s ACCA-accredited BCom (Professional) is the answer.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_ACCA_Qualification_15_Papers_Across_3_Levels\"><\/span><strong>The ACCA Qualification: 15 Papers Across 3 Levels<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ACCA comprises 15 papers across three levels where 13 are mandatory and 2 are chosen as electives at the Strategic Professional level.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Level 1 \u2014 Applied Knowledge (3 mandatory papers): <\/strong>Business and Technology (BT), Management Accounting (MA), and Financial Accounting (FA). These cover core business concepts, costing, budgeting, and foundational financial statements.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Level 2 \u2014 Applied Skills (6 mandatory papers): <\/strong>Corporate and Business Law (LW), Performance Management (PM), Taxation (TX), Financial Reporting (FR), Audit and Assurance (AA), and Financial Management (FM). This level moves into complex technical scenarios across law, audit, and financial management.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Level 3 \u2014 Strategic Professional (4 papers: 2 mandatory + 2 elective): <\/strong>Strategic Business Leader (SBL) and Strategic Business Reporting (SBR) are mandatory. Students choose 2 from Advanced Financial Management (AFM), Advanced Performance Management (APM), Advanced Taxation (ATX), and Advanced Audit and Assurance (AAA).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_MAHE_BCom_Professional_Integrates_with_ACCA\"><\/span><strong>How MAHE BCom (Professional) Integrates with ACCA<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>MAHE&#8217;s ACCA-accredited curriculum delivers two distinct categories of benefit to students:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Exemption from 9 ACCA papers: <\/strong>Students who complete the relevant BCom subjects are exempt from sitting all three Applied Knowledge and all six Applied Skills papers.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>In-curriculum training for 4 Strategic Professional papers: <\/strong>These papers cannot be exempted and must be attempted by all ACCA candidates. However, MAHE provides structured training, study material, and guidance from qualified ACCA trainers within the degree itself.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The 9 exempted papers span every Applied Knowledge and Applied Skills paper: BT, MA, FA, LW, PM, TX, FR, AA, and FM (refer table below). This means MAHE graduates begin their ACCA journey at the very top, that is, the Strategic Professional level, where the real distinction lies and where most candidates spend the most preparation time.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For 4 Strategic Professional papers, MAHE provides free study material delivered through a combination of academic faculty and qualified ACCA trainers. SBL and SBR are covered as mandatory training within the curriculum; APM and AFM are covered in semesters 5 and 6 respectively.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To fully appreciate the depth of MAHE&#8217;s BCom (Professional) program, here is the complete subject-by-subject curriculum across all six semesters, showing how ACCA-aligned subjects are woven throughout the degree:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th><strong>Semester<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>Subjects<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>ACCA Relevance<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>Credits<\/strong><\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"5\"><strong>Semester 1<\/strong><\/td><td><strong>Business and Technology (BT)<\/strong><\/td><td rowspan=\"5\"><strong>BT, FA, MA<\/strong> \u2014 All three Applied Knowledge papers covered and exempted<\/td><td rowspan=\"5\">4 each = 20 total<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Financial Accounting (FA)<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Management Accounting (MA)<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Business Communication<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Managerial Economics<\/td><\/tr><tr><td rowspan=\"5\"><strong>Semester 2<\/strong><\/td><td>Business Statistics and Mathematics<\/td><td rowspan=\"5\"><strong>FR and TX<\/strong> \u2014 Applied Skills papers covered and exempted<\/td><td rowspan=\"5\">4 each = 20 total<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Financial Reporting (FR)<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Taxation (TX)<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Analytics using Computer Applications<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Environmental Studies<\/td><\/tr><tr><td rowspan=\"5\"><strong>Semester 3<\/strong><\/td><td><strong>Audit and Assurance (AA)<\/strong><\/td><td rowspan=\"5\"><strong>AA, FM, LW \u2013 <\/strong>Applied Skills covered and exempted<br><br><strong>SBR \u2013 <\/strong>Strategic Professional training begins<\/td><td rowspan=\"5\">4 each = 20 total<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Financial Management (FM)<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Corporate and Business Law (LW)<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Strategic Business Reporting (SBR)<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Cybersecurity in Finance<\/td><\/tr><tr><td rowspan=\"7\"><strong>Semester 4<\/strong><\/td><td><strong>Performance Management (PM)<\/strong><\/td><td rowspan=\"7\"><strong>PM<\/strong> \u2013 exempted \u00a0 <br><strong>SBL<\/strong> \u2013 training \u00a0 \u00a0<\/td><td rowspan=\"7\">4 each = 20 total<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Strategic Business Leader (SBL)<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Marketing Management<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Operations Management<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><em>Electives: Choose ONE<\/em><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Project Management<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Indian Taxation<\/td><\/tr><tr><td rowspan=\"5\"><strong>Semester 5<\/strong><\/td><td>Research Methodology<\/td><td rowspan=\"5\"><strong>APM \u2013<\/strong> training \u00a0 <br><br><strong>AAA \u2013 <\/strong>training<\/td><td rowspan=\"5\">4 each = 20 total<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Sustainable Business Models and Circular Economy<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Advanced Performance Management (APM)<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Advanced Audit and Assurance (AAA)<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Project &#8211; I<\/td><\/tr><tr><td rowspan=\"7\"><strong>Semester 6<\/strong><\/td><td>International Business Management<\/td><td rowspan=\"7\"><strong>AFM <\/strong>\u2014 optional training<\/td><td rowspan=\"7\">4 each = 20 total<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Corporate Governance and Business Ethics<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Security Analysis &amp; Portfolio Management<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><em>Electives: Choose ONE<\/em><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Advanced Financial Management (AFM)<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Entrepreneurship and Startup Ecosystem<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>Project &#8211; II<\/td><\/tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\">TOTAL CREDITS<\/td><td>120<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Accreditation_Validity_and_What_It_Means_for_You\"><\/span><strong>Accreditation Validity and What It Means for You<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>MAHE&#8217;s ACCA accreditation is valid for students graduating between 2029 and 2033. Students enrolling now and completing the standard three-year program will graduate within this window, making their exemption certificates fully valid. The accreditation is institutional and if you graduate during the valid period, your exemptions are secure.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If your graduation or ACCA registration is delayed beyond 2033, a membership renewal fee will be required to maintain exemption validity. The practical advice is simple: register with ACCA promptly upon graduation, claim your exemptions, and pay the per-paper exemption fees within 30 days of them being awarded to your MyACCA account.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Financial_Case_What_MAHE_Saves_You\"><\/span><strong>The Financial Case: What MAHE Saves You<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The decision to pursue the MAHE BCom (Professional) over a traditional BCom followed by standalone ACCA study is not just about time, it is a significant financial decision. Here is a comprehensive comparison:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th><strong>Expenses<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>BCom without ACCA<\/strong><\/th><th><strong>ACCA integrated BCom (MAHE)<\/strong><\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td>BCom Degree Fee (3 Years)<\/td><td>INR 100,000 \u2013 INR 300,000<\/td><td>INR 294,000<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>ACCA Registration Fee<\/td><td>INR 3,500 \u2013 INR 10,500* \u00a0 <br><br><sub>*ACCA may offer discounts from time to time<\/sub><\/td><td>INR 2400* \u00a0 <br><br><sub>*Discounted fee only for students of BCom (Professional) ACCA accredited<\/sub><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>ACCA Annual Subscription<\/td><td>INR 15,800 x 3 = \u20b947,400<\/td><td>INR 15,800 x 2* = INR 31,600<br><br><sub>*First year subscription is exempted.<\/sub><\/td><\/tr><tr><td>ACCA Exam Fees (13 Papers)<\/td><td>Applied Knowledge (3 papers): INR 30,000 \u2013 INR 40,800 <br><br>Applied Skills (6 papers): INR 102,000 \u2013 259,800 <br><br>Strategic Professional (4 papers): INR 94,000 \u2013 INR 192,000 \u00a0 <br><br><strong>Total Fee:<\/strong> INR 226,000 \u2013 INR 492,600*<br><br><sub>*Depends on mode of exam or entry time<\/sub><\/td><td>Applied Knowledge (3 papers): <em>Exempted<\/em> <br><br>Applied Skills (6 papers): <em>Exempted<\/em> <br><br>Strategic Professional (4 papers): INR 94,000 <strong>\u00a0<\/strong> <br><br><strong>Total Fee: <\/strong>INR 94,000<\/td><\/tr><tr><td>ACCA Coaching (Optional)<\/td><td>INR 130,000- INR 260,000* \u00a0 <br><br><sub>*Depends on institution or mode of study<\/sub><\/td><td>Included* \u00a0 <br><br><sub>*Training provided by faculty + Qualified ACCA trainers<\/sub><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Total Estimated Cost<\/strong><\/td><td><strong>INR 5.07 \u2013 INR 11.10 lakhs<\/strong><\/td><td><strong>INR 4.22 lakhs<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Time Required<\/strong><strong><\/strong><\/td><td><strong>5\u20136 years (BCom + ACCA prep)<\/strong><strong><\/strong><\/td><td><strong>3 years BCom + 1 year for 4 Strategic Papers<\/strong><\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Complete_Pathway_to_Full_ACCA_Membership\"><\/span><strong>The Complete Pathway to Full ACCA Membership<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Earning exemptions is the beginning, not the end. Here is the roadmap from MAHE enrolment to full ACCA membership:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">Stage<\/th><th>Step<\/th><th>Description<\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">1<\/td><td>Complete MAHE BCom (Professional)<\/td><td>Three-year online program covering all Applied Knowledge and Applied Skills content, with Strategic Professional training embedded in the curriculum.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">2<\/td><td>Register with ACCA and Claim Exemptions<\/td><td>Register at accaglobal.com, submit your degree and transcripts, and apply for all 9 exemptions. Pay exemption fees within 30 days. MAHE students pay a discounted registration fee of INR 2,400.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">3<\/td><td>Complete the Ethics and Professional Skills Module (EPSM)<\/td><td>This is an online self-paced module of approximately 20 hours. It can be started after completing Applied Knowledge and should ideally be done before sitting the SBL exam.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">4<\/td><td>Sit and Pass 4 Strategic Professional Papers<\/td><td>SBL and SBR are mandatory; choose 2 from AFM, APM, ATX, and AAA.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">5<\/td><td>Achieve ACCA Affiliate Status<\/td><td>Upon passing all 13 papers and completing the EPSM, you become an ACCA Affiliate.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">6<\/td><td>Complete the Practical Experience Requirement (PER)<\/td><td>This includes 36 months of supervised, relevant work experience across 5 Essential and 4 Technical performance objectives, signed off by your workplace mentor.<\/td><\/tr><tr><td class=\"has-text-align-center\" data-align=\"center\">7<\/td><td>Apply for Full ACCA Membership<\/td><td>Submit PER evidence and EPSM completion. Pay the one-time admission fee that will let you use &#8216;ACCA&#8217; after your name, recognised in 181 countries.<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Career_Opportunities_After_Graduation\"><\/span><strong>Career Opportunities After Graduation<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/online-bcom-professional-mahe\">MAHE BCom (Professional)<\/a> graduates enter the job market positioned for roles that typically require several more years of study from candidates on traditional commerce routes. The ACCA qualification is actively sought by employers across Professional Services (Big 4: Deloitte, PwC, EY, KPMG), Banking and Financial Services, Public Sector, FinTech, Retail, Pharmaceuticals, and more. Because ACCA is recognised in 181 countries, graduates also have access to international job markets in the UK, UAE, Singapore, Canada, and Australia \u2014 without requiring additional requalification.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"The_Smartest_Start_to_a_Global_Finance_Career\"><\/span><strong>The Smartest Start to a Global Finance Career<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The MAHE <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/online-bcom-professional-mahe\">Online BCom (Professional)<\/a> with ACCA accreditation is not merely an upgraded commerce degree. It is a carefully engineered pathway that builds global professional readiness into the undergraduate curriculum itself. By the time you graduate, you will have covered the equivalent of 9 ACCA exams through your coursework, received in-curriculum training for 4 Strategic Professional papers, and positioned yourself to achieve full ACCA qualification. For anyone serious about a career in finance, whether in India or internationally, this is the place to start.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Frequently_Asked_Questions_FAQs\"><\/span><strong>Frequently Asked Questions<\/strong> <strong>(FAQs)<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Q1. What does ACCA accreditation mean for MAHE&#8217;s Online BCom (Professional)?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>ACCA&#8217;s Professional Qualifications Approvals team has assessed MAHE&#8217;s curriculum and confirmed that specific subjects are equivalent in content and depth to specific ACCA exam papers, granting students the right to claim exemptions from those papers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Q2. Is MAHE&#8217;s accreditation valid for my graduation year?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, the accreditation covers graduates from 2029 to 2033. Students enrolling now and completing the standard three-year program will graduate within this window.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Q3. Is ACCA registration automatic upon completing my BCom?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>No, you must register independently at accaglobal.com, provide your qualification documents, and apply for exemptions yourself.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Q4. Which 9 papers am I exempted from through MAHE&#8217;s BCom?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>All three Applied Knowledge papers (BT, MA, FA) and all six Applied Skills papers (LW, PM, TX, FR, AA, FM). Training is provided for 4 Strategic Professional papers (SBL, SBR, AFM, APM).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Q5. Are there fees for claiming the 9 exemptions?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, ACCA charges a per-paper exemption fee for all 9 papers, payable within 30 days of exemptions beingawarded to your MyACCA account.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Q6. What are the key fees for MAHE students pursuing ACCA?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Registration (INR 2,400 discounted), annual subscription (INR 12,000\u201316,000, first year waived for MAHE students), per-paper exemption fees, Strategic Professional exam fees, and the EPSM module fee.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Q7. Does my exemption certificate expire if I delay registration?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>MAHE&#8217;s accreditation runs to 2033. Register with ACCA and claim exemptions within this window; delaying beyond 2033 may require a re-validation fee.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Q8. Can I work internationally with my MAHE BCom and ACCA qualification?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, upon completing the 4 Strategic Professional papers, your ACCA Affiliate or Member designation is recognised in 181 countries, particularly valued in the UK, UAE, Singapore, Canada, and Australia.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Q9. What documents do I need to submit to ACCA to claim my exemptions?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You need to submit your MAHE BCom (Professional) degree certificate and official academic transcripts in English, along with a valid photo ID.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Q10. How do I verify my exemption eligibility before applying?<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can use ACCA&#8217;s Exemptions Calculator at accaglobal.com. Search for &#8216;Manipal Academy of Higher Education,&#8217; and view the exact exemptions available for the BCom (Professional) program.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>9 Exemptions. Training for 4 Papers. One Degree That Does It All. Imagine finishing your BCom degree and walking out the door already exempt from 9 out of 13 ACCA exams \u2013 papers that ordinarily take other candidates one to two additional years to clear. That is exactly what MAHE&#8217;s Online BCom (Professional) program, now [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":124,"featured_media":17480196,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[612],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-17479439","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-bcom"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v27.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/product\/yoast-seo-wordpress\/ -->\n<title>Online BCom (Professional): Your Fast-Track to ACCA Qualification- Online Manipal<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"MAHE&#039;s Online BCom (Professional) is ACCA-accredited and grants 9 paper exemptions. Finish your degree and your ACCA qualification at the same time.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17479439\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Online BCom (Professional): Your Fast-Track to ACCA Qualification- Online Manipal\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"MAHE&#039;s Online BCom (Professional) is ACCA-accredited and grants 9 paper exemptions. Finish your degree and your ACCA qualification at the same time.\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/online-bcom-professional-acca-accredited\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Online Manipal\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:publisher\" content=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\